# Build output 此文件可以用来过滤构建过程中生成的文件和目录，避免将它们提交到版本控制系统中。以下是一些常见的构建输出和临时文件的示例：
/build/
/bin/
/CMakeFiles/
/CMakeCache.txt
/Makefile
/Makefile.*
/cmake_install.cmake
/tempCode
# IDE / editor
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln
*.vcxproj*

# Logs
*.log

# Generated files
*.o
*.obj
*.exe
*.out

# Temporary files
*~
.DS_Store
